<item>
            <title>[MNG-579] a dependency of type tld is not added to the package</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-579</link>
                <project id="12316922" key="MNG">Maven (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;the project package is set to &apos;war&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;a dependency is added as follows:&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;dependency&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;groupId&amp;gt;spring&amp;lt;/groupId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;artifactId&amp;gt;spring&amp;lt;/artifactId&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;version&amp;gt;1.0.2&amp;lt;/version&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;scope&amp;gt;runtime&amp;lt;/scope&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
  &amp;lt;type&amp;gt;tld&amp;lt;/type&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/dependency&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;running  &apos;m2 clean:clean package&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
does NOT add the spring-1.0.2.tld to the war file&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
                <environment>Windows XP SP2 jdk 5.0</environment>
